<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Grow Together ðŸŒ¿</title>

  <!-- Google Fonts -->
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- Bootstrap -->
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

  <!-- Custom CSS -->
  <style>
    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Poppins', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #f0fdf4 0%, #dcfce7 50%, #bbf7d0 100%);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    .hero-container {
      background: white;
      border-radius: 24px;
      box-shadow: 0 20px 60px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      padding: 4rem 3rem;
      max-width: 600px;
      width: 100%;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      position: relative;
      overflow: hidden;
    }

    .hero-container::before {
      content: '';
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      right: 0;
      height: 4px;
      background: linear-gradient(90deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
    }

    .hero-container:hover {
      transform: translateY(-5px);
      box-shadow: 0 25px 70px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
    }

    h1 {
      font-weight: 700;
      font-size: 2.5rem;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
      -webkit-background-clip: text;
      -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
      background-clip: text;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
      letter-spacing: -1px;
    }

    p {
      color: #64748b;
      margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .btn-custom {
      padding: 0.9rem 2.5rem;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 1rem;
      transition: all 0.3s ease;
      text-decoration: none;
      display: inline-block;
    }

    .btn-login {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #22c55e 0%, #16a34a 100%);
      color: white;
      border: none;
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.3);
    }

    .btn-login:hover {
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 15px 40px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.4);
    }

    .btn-signup {
      background: white;
      border: 2px solid #22c55e;
      color: #16a34a;
    }

    .btn-signup:hover {
      background: #f0fdf4;
      transform: translateY(-3px);
      box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2);
    }

    .illustration {
      width: 140px;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      animation: float 3s ease-in-out infinite;
      filter: drop-shadow(0 10px 20px rgba(34, 197, 94, 0.2));
    }

    @keyframes float {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0); }
      50% { transform: translateY(-15px); }
    }

    .btn-group {
      display: flex;
      gap: 1rem;
      justify-content: center;
      flex-wrap: wrap;
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="hero-container">
    <img src="/images/plant.png" alt="Plant icon" class="illustration">
    <h1>Grow Together ðŸŒ¿</h1>
    <p>Plant small habits. Grow a beautiful life.<br>Start nurturing your personal garden of growth today.</p>

    <div class="btn-group">
      <a href="/login" class="btn-custom btn-login">Login</a>
      <a href="/signup" class="btn-custom btn-signup">Sign Up</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
